Constructor Detail

Plus

public Plus(java.lang.Class<T> c)
Builds Plus functor for the given class. The class argument must be the same as the generic class argument (when generics are in use) or else a ClassCastException will be thrown when the functor is used.

Throws:
java.lang.IllegalArgumentException - if the given class has no Arithmetic implementation registered with the ArithmeticFactory
